room_title: Escape room "Jail Break" by Locked & Coded in Charleston (WV)
review: We played the Jail Break room and it was so fun! If you haven't tried the Locked and Coded escape room, you are missing out! The staff was extremely nice, the game was well thought out and the theme was extremely on point! Thanks for a fun Friday night!

room_title: Escape room "Jail Break" by Locked & Coded in Charleston (WV)
review: Had a great time with the Jail Break room. The solutions were just the right difficulty... Not too easy, but not too hard. Timely hints helped when we got stuck on one part of the escape. Great team-building activity for a small group.

room_title: Escape room "Jail Break" by Locked & Coded in Charleston (WV)
review: This was amazing! My team and I completed Jail Break with 14 min left. Would totally recommend!

room_title: Escape room "Jail Break" by Locked & Coded in Charleston (WV)
review: Did this last night with friends and it was so much fun! We did Jail Break and it was harder and more fun than I even expected. Can't wait til next time!
